,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:46:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e09715ceb492edc6a665efa78131836374dd7f1a","tid":1742672,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cf43cc393ba6327c8101003e7eb1f50e251f262","tid":1742672,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09715ceb492edc6a665efa78131836374dd7f1a","tid":1742672,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"情報系統 哨兵系統需要全面升級：屋企私家cam<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/adBicwV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/adBicwV</a><br />\n#16 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我既立意係自己睇完報哨兵台，而唔係畀一個完全身份不明既人mon，問題係邊入面有講，而且有手捉講得好會連black bloc都畀人睇撚埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係驚老豆搵仔被狗滲透/頂替左既話<br />\n首先 ，隻cam 唔好廿四小時畀人睇<br />\n第二，隻cam要zoom到只對路中心，唔好影其他大廈單位，調教角度後避免起到真實地址<br />\n第三，即使信任老豆搵仔都好，隻cam只要夠低清就乜柒都睇唔到，<br />\nset cam目標:睇清狗車動向，落左地既其實唔需要睇得清，set幾清，方向自己話事<br />\n<br />\n你可以用我觀點完整下出畀其他channel投稿"},{"pid":"e851a516930f11a9bf5464d759ab5af06c190cac","tid":1742672,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"要改密碼"},{"pid":"25100fcecf0c32fbc73a71fc5dd95e56a088721f","tid":1742672,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98ce570b74bdfa1ce109dc6bca7aa0af189a8e3b","tid":1742672,"uid":15084,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c5fac02f38e3b2b5ce504242173c9c2f659d5eb0","tid":1742672,"uid":65328,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2b016cb4d1c3023e96426e309c65f063beeb1990","tid":1742672,"uid":317795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"邊個提議放link咁白痴？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"一個組織有所有link係好撚危險"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"其實裝cam ok，但自己留底就算<